---
title: Speedy Caribbean Jerk Pork Tacos with Charred Corn & Pineapple Salsa
description: Take your tastebuds on a holiday tonight! With gentle heat from the jerk seasoning, tanginess from the garlic aioli and a touch of smokey flavour from the charred corn, this meal will bring a tropical island vibe to your dinner table.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5d2fee805839a100164453e1-8bd7da1e.jpg
